title: The Punisher V.5 Marvel MAX #72 - Welcome to the Bayou: Part 2
description:
Punisher - Frank Castle Max 72

'WELCOME TO THE BAYOU,' PART 2 OF 4.
by Gischler, Parlov, and Loughridge

"Traveling the Louisiana back roads with something awful stored in his trunk, Frank Castle stops at a service station on the edge of the bayou--and steps into a world of unspeakable horror.

Patrolling the depths of hell, the Punisher has crossed paths with some unsavory characters, but noting has prepared him for the unspeakable depravity of the Geautreauxs."
